rows.label: tlk4171015101_msg0001
rows.name:
I'm so happy to be living with my
sons. I never thought I would be
able to live like this again.

rows.label: tlk4171015101_msg0002
rows.name:
It's all thanks to you
and Elnoth. Thank you.

rows.label: tlk4171015101_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm going to work hard enough that we'll be
fine even when Elnoth gets back from the Empire,
and we'll all live together as a family.
